4 A BILL
5 TO BE ENTITLED
6 AN ACT
7
8
9 Relating to Houston County; to further provide for the
10 sale or redemption of lands for taxes.
11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
12 Section 1. In Houston County, any duties of the judge
13 of probate relating to the selling or redeeming of lands for
14 taxes shall be transferred to and performed by the revenue
15 commissioner, and the judge of probate shall be relieved of
16 all related duties
17 Section 2. This act shall become effective immediately.
